{"tid":475654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騙佣呃客　California健身教練判囚","createTime":"2017-11-21T10:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T10:13:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3633a82fe2e43afcc7dc7c3fca6923448ccbeda1","tid":475654,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171121/20220693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20220693&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=68137250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20220693&h=1ade8b85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171121/20220693</a><br />\n<br />\n騙佣呃客　California健身教練判囚<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171121/large/17975279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F17975279.jpg&h=adddc35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕭潤基（右）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】已停業的健身中心California Fitness，一名健身教練及其下屬誘騙女顧客簽下5萬元私人教練協議，又向公司提交虛假協議書，騙取6,000元佣金。健身教練早前被裁定欺詐及串謀使用虛假文書3罪罪成。辯方昨稱被告只是「疏忽冇跟進」單據，裁判官反駁是有意圖欺詐，判他入獄5個月。<br />\n<br />\n案發於2012年9月，辯方求情指被告蕭潤基（33歲）犯案時年輕，舊公司讚他表現佳，若被告做多一步向公司申請，或不會導致事件。惟裁判官反駁，被告不是因疏忽而被定罪，他有份參與及容許下屬欺詐。另一被告潘偉峰是蕭下屬，他早前承認兩項欺詐罪，轉污點證人稍後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC609/17<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"}]}